dc_title_s: Michigan; prepared by Henry S. Stebbins.
dc_description_s: Includes insets of Isle Royale and of the western half of the Upper Peninsula. Shows railroads. On verso: Population of the United States in 1870 and 1880 by counties. 1 map: col.; 55 x 40 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
